Geographical occurrence.
This species is found in the &lt;a href="United%20States"&gt;United States of America&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="South%20Africa"&gt;South Africa&lt;/a&gt;.
Clinical features and host pathology.
Hosts of this species include domestic &lt;a href="turkey%20%28bird%29"&gt;turkey&lt;/a&gt;s ("&lt;a href="Meleagris%20gallopavo"&gt;Meleagris gallopavo&lt;/a&gt;") and Swainson's &lt;a href="Francolin"&gt;Francolin&lt;/a&gt; ("&lt;a href="Francolinus%20swainsoni"&gt;Francolinus swainsoni&lt;/a&gt;").
